title: Hazure Skill "Kage ga Usui" wo Motsu Guild Shokuin ga, Jitsu wa Densetsu no Ansatsusha
title_english: Hazure Skill: The Guild Member with a Worthless Skill Is Actually a Legendary Assassin
title_japanese: 外れスキル「影が薄い」を持つギルド職員が、実は伝説の暗殺者
title_synonyms: The guild official with weak skill "VANISH" is actually legendary assassin
synopsis:
After defeating the demon lord, assassin Roland seems destined for eternal greatness, yet he wants nothing of the sort! Determined to avoid fame and fortune in pursuit of a normal life, he applies for a job at the local Adventurers Guild, where all manner of intrepid warriors come to turn in their quests. But Roland has no idea what "normal" really is, and he's anything but your average employee! Will this world-class assassin be able to adjust to the monotony of everyday life at the guild?

(Source: Yen Press)
background: Hazure Skill "Kage ga Usui" wo Motsu Guild Shokuin ga, Jitsu wa Densetsu no Ansatsusha has been published in English as Hazure Skill: The Guild Member with a Worthless Skill Is Actually a Legendary Assassin by Yen Press since May 4, 2021.
